✍ Stream (Buffer Area) ==> IO (InputStream (read) / OutputStream (Write))
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

											✍ Types of Stream ✍ 
											---------------------
													  |
			--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
			|										  |											 |
	1) InputStream (read)					2) OutputStream (Write)						3) ErrorStream
	►  System.in							►  System.out.println();					►  System.err

		
⦿	InputStream (read) :-				
----------------------

► System.in --> Default InputStream ---> Console 
► ex..

					read(InputStream)
	Program <----------------------------- Console

	Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
 	int no = sc.nextInt();


⦿	OutputStream (Write) :-				
------------------------
► System.out --> Default OutputStream ---> Console 
► ex..

					Write(OutputStream)
	Program <----------------------------- Console
	
	System.out.println("Hello");


⦿	ErrorStream :-				
------------------------
► System.err --> Default ErrorStream ---> Console 

► ex..

					error(ErrorStream)
	Program <----------------------------- Console
	
	System.err.println("Hello");

