⦿	Data :-
---------
► There are Two Types of Data is available.

				
					String							UDO(User Define Objects[Student/Employee/Person/Product])
					------							---------------------------------------------------------
		1) Byte Oriented Way 						1) Byte Oriented Way 	
			► read (FileInputStream) 	                ► read (FileInputStream) 
			► write (FileOutputStream)                  ► write (FileOutputStream)
		
		2) Character Oriented Way 		
			► read (FileReader) 	
			► write (FileWriter)		
					

































		